OL,3,CThree-year-old mauled 'after being
OL,4,Callowed to climb XL bully'
OL,6,FA three-year-old boy was mauled by his
OL,7,Ffamily's XL bully after being allowed
OL,8,Fto try to climb onto the dog's back,
OL,9,Fpolice have said.
OL,11,FThe boy needed surgery after being
OL,12,Fbitten on the face by the legally
OL,13,Fregistered dog in Doncaster.
OL,15,FSouth Yorkshire Police said the
OL,16,Fincident, on Monday 18 March, happened
OL,17,F"after parents and guardians allowed
OL,18,Fthe child to attempt to climb the dog".
OL,20,FParamedics found him "seriously
OL,21,Fbleeding".
