OL,6,FHe was taken to hospital, for surgery
OL,7,Fto his wounds.
OL,9,FIt became a criminal offence in
OL,10,FFebruary to own an unregistered XL
OL,11,Fbully.
OL,13,FCh Insp Emma Cheney said: "This family
OL,14,Fhave acknowledged the change in
OL,15,Flegislation around the XL bully and
OL,16,Fregistered their dog, but this doesn't
OL,17,Fremove the danger that these dogs pose
OL,18,Fand why the ban has come into place.
