OL,4,Callowed to climb XL bully'
OL,6,F"All dogs can be aggressive. They are
OL,7,Fanimals, but some dogs have greater
OL,8,Fcapability to cause harm due to their
OL,9,Fsize and strength.
OL,11,F"Children should never be unsupervised
OL,12,Fwhen with dogs, even family pets that
OL,13,Fyou believe would never hurt your
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,F"A dog's instinct to protect itself is
OL,17,Fto bite. Parents should ensure
OL,18,Fchildren learn to respect a dog's
OL,19,Fspace and be encouraged to have
OL,20,Fboundaries around feeding and resting
OL,21,Ftimes."
