OL,6,FThe dog was seized by police and
OL,7,Fremains in kennels while
OL,8,Finvestigations continue.
OL,10,FCh Inspector Cheney added: "An
OL,11,Fincident like this is a stark reminder
OL,12,Fthat regardless of a dog's nature, or
OL,13,Fprevious interactions with children,
OL,14,Fother dogs and people, they are
OL,15,Fanimals and their innate instinct is
OL,16,Fto protect themselves which can result
OL,17,Fin serious injuries and sometimes
OL,18,Ffatality."
